## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the inherent biases present in the sources. Some sources may reflect particular ideological stances, which could influence the presentation of arguments. Additionally, the complexity of legal systems and cultural differences across regions may affect the applicability of these findings universally. Further research could provide more nuanced insights into the death penalty's impact and legality.